<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>I'm Sorry</title>

    <style>
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body{
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #cfe8ff, #eaf5ff);
            display:flex;
            justify-content:center;
            align-items:center;
            min-height:100vh;
            text-align:center;
            padding:20px;
        }

        .card{
            background:white;
            padding:40px;
            border-radius:25px;
            max-width:650px;
            box-shadow:0 15px 35px rgba(80,140,255,0.15);
        }

        .cat{
            width:150px;
            margin-bottom:15px;
            animation: float 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float{
            50%{
                transform:translateY(-8px);
            }
        }

        h1{
            color:#4a8cff;
            margin-bottom:15px;
        }

        p{
            color:#555;
            line-height:1.8;
            margin-bottom:15px;
        }

        button{
            background:#6ea8fe;
            color:white;
            border:none;
            padding:12px 25px;
            border-radius:30px;
            cursor:pointer;
            font-size:16px;
            margin-top:10px;
            transition:0.3s;
        }

        button:hover{
            background:#4a8cff;
            transform:scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">

    <!-- Make sure image(10).png is in the same folder as this HTML file -->
    <img src="c:\Users\user\Downloads\download.png" alt="Sad Cat" class="cat">

    <h1>Hii Gab! 💙</h1>

    <p>
        uhm I just wanted to say sorry about kanina. I didn't mean to
        share the things na nalaman ko kay Junette earlier. It was very
        immature of me po and I really regret doing that.
    </p>

    <p>
        About din po sa cut off, sana po hindi muna. I'm really not ready
        for that po. It really hurts my heart po talaga and naiiyak ako
        every time you say na mag-cut off na tayo. Hindi pa po talaga ako
        ready.
    </p>

    <p>
        I was coding this at 2 AM because I honestly didn't know what to do.
        I've been crying since kanina and naisipan ko nalang gumawa ng website
        both to practice and to tell you how sorry I am.
    </p>

    <p>
        I know saying sorry won't automatically fix everything, but I hope
        you know that I genuinely mean it. I appreciate you a lot, and I
        don't want my mistake to be the reason we lose our friendship.
    </p>

    <button onclick="showMessage()">Click Me</button>

</div>

<script>
function showMessage(){
    alert("I'm really sorry po, Gab. I know I messed up and I understand if you're hurt. I just hope we can still fix things. 🥹💙");
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
